Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.07,0:01:04.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.07,0:01:04.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't see
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.44,0:01:05.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:05.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't see
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.30,0:01:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.05,0:01:09.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.05,0:01:09.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Papa
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.70,0:01:10.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:10.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:26.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(938,570)}炸药厂
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.23,0:01:26.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村期待已久的炸药厂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.23,0:01:26.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bikini Bottom's long-awaited dynamite factory
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在开业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:28.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is now open
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.10,0:01:29.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:29.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.26,0:01:40.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师  从上面可以看到你家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:40.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mrs. Puff, I can see your house from up here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:52.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at that
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.22,0:01:54.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮我省下了往返通勤的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:54.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You saved me a commute
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.17,0:01:56.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还是先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:56.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just let yourself out
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.55,0:01:58.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你确定的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:58.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you're sure
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.26,0:02:00.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天再见  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:00.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.19,0:02:06.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可能真的完全教不会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:06.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe he really is unteachable
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.22,0:02:09.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:09.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I give up
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.20,0:02:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.02,0:02:12.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:12.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not yet
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.17,0:02:14.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可是个驾校教练
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:14.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a driving instructor
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.27,0:02:17.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,教导那小子可是你的重责大任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:17.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Instructing that boy is your duty
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你只需要一点引导就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:21.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just need a little guidance
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宇宙向你问好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The universe greets you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.77,0:02:32.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我来引导你的天体运动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:32.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to guide your celestial vessel
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,driving
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.03,0:02:35.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:35.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.96,0:02:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疯掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.72,0:02:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想脱离你这种状况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it would help
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.45,0:02:46.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就需要想办法陪着海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:46.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you find a way to be with SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但同时又不在海绵宝宝身边  行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without being with SpongeBob, hmm?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.87,0:02:51.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:51.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.31,0:02:53.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎你以后再来用钱来烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:53.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feel free to annoy me for money again soon
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.87,0:02:54.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:54.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodbye
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,压力少点了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:03.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Less stress
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陪着海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Being with SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.57,0:03:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,同时又不在海绵宝宝身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without being with SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.27,0:03:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.35,0:03:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,音乐从哪传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is that music coming from?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A submarine?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That gives me an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.16,0:03:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有水手的地方都会有土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where there are sailors, there are always potatoes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:50.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(734,440)}小尖尖玻璃刀
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Qu'est-ce que c'est?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.45,0:04:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样应该能成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That should do it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's been so long
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.62,0:04:22.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很想我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:22.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you miss me?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.95,0:04:26.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可太想了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:26.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是想死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I missed you so much
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴能再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's so good to see you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.52,0:04:32.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从这见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:32.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from here
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你买了新帽子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you get a new hat?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.82,0:04:37.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,显得你眼睛更漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:37.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It really brings out all your eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.50,0:04:46.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该专心看路了  我的优秀小笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:46.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to focus on the road, my excellent little noodle
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定不会辜负你期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must live up to your noodle-spectations
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.64,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1354,714)}起点
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.64,0:04:57.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,表现太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:57.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was very good
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.30,0:05:00.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  在这边右转
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:00.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, take a right here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在继续右转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now keep going right
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feels right to me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, it does
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.08,0:05:13.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在能补剧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:13.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I can catch up on my stories
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.86,0:05:16.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,德韦恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:16.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dwayne
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.65,0:05:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我唯一的心之所爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only thing I've ever loved
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.81,0:05:21.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是把你脑袋砸得四分五裂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:21.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is a skull-cracking smackdown
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1024,924)}右
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一直右转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep going right?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.66,0:05:28.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:28.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:29.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  感觉我真的快掌握
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, I really feel like I'm getting the hang
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,右转的技巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of this turning-right thing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都破我开船不出船祸最长时间记录了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the longest I've ever driven without crashing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个都不剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's none left
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Left
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(924,922)}左
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,左转
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Left?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.27,0:05:46.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我还在练右转啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:46.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm still working on right
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真觉得我做好准备了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you really think I'm ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(672,234)}慢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:49.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1652,454)}小心驾驶
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.79,0:05:50.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:50.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.23,0:05:53.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  那我就左转了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:53.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, if you think so
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有些人真是费尽心思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some people will do anything
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想开进多乘员专用道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to use the carpool lane
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:18.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,868)}享用
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.95,0:06:27.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:27.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.17,0:06:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的车技完美无瑕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your driving is immaculate
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.75,0:06:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一直右转就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just keep turning right
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个我很会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm great at that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:42.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(450,968)}上品瓷器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:54.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1030,294)}裤头村监狱
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.91,0:06:49.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,右转要开得稳稳的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:49.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep that righty nice and tight-y
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,稳稳右转
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tightening my rightening
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.80,0:07:02.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天一定是我当教练以来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:02.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the most fulfilling day
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.13,0:07:04.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最满意的一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've ever had as a teacher
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.51,0:07:10.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你吞到虫子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:10.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Swallowed a bug, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.69,0:07:15.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各单位注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:15.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention all units--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正在发生严重交通违法行为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,major traffic violations in progress
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请尽快追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please pursue as fast as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:21.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1256,480)}停
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1264,808)}学员驾驶员
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.12,0:07:26.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一定就是进阶课程了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:26.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This must be an advanced lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:34.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(576,248)}多节指关节\N每夜都打架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:34.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1420,424)}酒馆
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.13,0:07:36.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:36.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's him--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旁边坐了个土豆的浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the jerk with the spud
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.80,0:07:39.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:39.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get him, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这座极具历史意义的炸药厂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This historic dynamite factory
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.87,0:07:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开业一整天以来都没出事故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has been open for one entire day with no accidents
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,插入通话  船员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Breaker, breaker, Cabin Boy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,左满舵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hard to port
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收到  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A 10-4, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都老得不想玩这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gettin' too old for this
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们中断摔跤夹头撕心裂肺电视剧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We interrupt "Headlocks and Heartbreaks"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(948,204)}裤头村快讯
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.62,0:08:35.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,插播一则紧急新闻快讯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:35.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with an emergency news bulletin
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.00,0:08:39.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超速海绵与土豆罪犯致全裤头村恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,High-speed sponge terrorizes Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with potato prisoner--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,群众最后目击到他在克拉肯大道上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,last seen pursued by band of bandit bikers
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被鬼火骑手追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,along Kraken Avenue
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁知道他接下来会袭击何处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who knows where he may strike next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1304,782)}突发新闻 疯子横冲直撞
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.57,0:08:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:04.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.89,0:09:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.35,0:09:11.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不戴这顶休闲假发了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:11.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough of this leisure wig
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.27,0:09:14.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改戴追杀假发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:14.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for the pursuit wig
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356,974)}情境式假发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1058,782)}火爆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:17.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1186,130)}火炮操纵杆
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是驾校教练
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a driving instructor
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.55,0:09:30.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要征用这辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:30.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'm commandeering this vehicle
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.15,0:09:32.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白  鸡冠头大妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:32.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can dig it, mohawk mama
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.77,0:09:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快掉头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Turn around
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1164,356)}肉汁
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你被削成泥了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've been mashed
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.62,0:10:35.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:35.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's alive
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你复原能力太强了  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure are resilient, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.61,0:10:40.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从现在起  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:40.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From now on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.55,0:10:43.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要负起驾校教练的重责大任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:43.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll uphold my duty as your driving instructor
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.62,0:10:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确保你行船安全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to keep you safe on the road
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.10,0:10:58.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是火爆泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:10:58.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're Puff the Tuff
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能在我石膏上面签名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you sign my cast?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.10,0:11:03.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一个神人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:03.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a legend
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.05,0:11:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看样子你们把事情都控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like you got things under control here
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's scram
Dialogue: 1,0:11:13.95,0:11:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,流程我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know the drill
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你干了什么才进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what are you in for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:31.21,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FF97&}万能神油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:32.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(697.802,374)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:32.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(711.802,668)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:37.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(771.802,666)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(631.802,464)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(743.802,534)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(565.802,506)}联合监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(659.802,540)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(578,414)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得好啊  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice work, boy-o
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.75,0:11:48.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王干净得不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:48.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She looks cleaner than a freshly scraped hull
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.85,0:11:49.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板好  我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:49.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mr. Krabs, I--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.66,0:11:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your feet
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was close
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你差点把黏液
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You almost tracked goo
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踩得干干净净的蟹堡王到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all over your nice, clean restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.40,0:12:05.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,补救得不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:05.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good save, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来这滩黏液就是罪魁祸首
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:14.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like this puddle here is the culprit
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.21,0:12:15.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:15.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mr. K
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.40,0:12:17.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一下子就能清理干净
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:17.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have her cleaned up in no time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:21.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(654,572)}洗洁精
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:30.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把这个倒进去  然后就
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you just pour this in here, and--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还说什么今天真是美好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"It's a beautiful day," you said
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.40,0:12:41.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还说什么得去外面搞什么邪恶科学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:41.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Why not do some evil science outside?" you said
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.67,0:12:42.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:42.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.70,0:12:45.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:45.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in Neptune's navel are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.02,0:12:52.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在帮蟹老板清理这滩黏液
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:52.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just cleaning up this goo puddle for Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.01,0:12:56.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着不像黏液
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:56.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That doesn't look like goo
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒像是石油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like oil
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊  凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy moly, Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们脚下就是金山银山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're sittin' on a mountain of moolah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.46,0:13:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石油是我的  听见没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That oil's mine, you hear?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.30,0:13:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我员工先发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My employee found it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.85,0:13:11.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还是在我地产上的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:11.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and besides, it's on me property
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先别急  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石油是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my oil
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.22,0:13:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还在我地产上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it's on my property
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(580,622)}咕噜
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实你们都说错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, you're both wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.73,0:13:31.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这根本不是石油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:31.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not oil at all
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根据我的分析
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,According to my analysis
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.93,0:13:39.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是蟹黄堡油与海霸糊流的混合物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's a combination of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:39.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty grease and Chum runoff
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你们两家餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which your two restaurants
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几十年来渗进地底下的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have been leaking into the ground for decades
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.85,0:13:47.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说这就是不值钱的地沟老油了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:47.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So it's just worthless old grease?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.34,0:13:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并不会不值钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't call it "worthless"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它有着极高的黏度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It has a high viscosity index
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.06,0:13:54.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有惊为天人的提味特性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:54.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and impressive flavor-imparting characteristics
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说很值钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So its "worthful"?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.77,0:13:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然而这滩地沟油似乎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,however, the deposit appears to be
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.80,0:14:02.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得两家平均分配才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:02.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,evenly split between your restaurants
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.20,0:14:04.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:04.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.62,0:14:07.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看样子要想赚大钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:07.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,looks like if we want to make a lot of money
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.17,0:14:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就必须得成为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll have to do it as
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,合作伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Partners
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:13.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,340)}合作伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}漫长的几天后
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.09,0:14:21.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西一定有咱俩公认的用途
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:21.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's got to be some use for this stuff we can agree on
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就卖给军方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's sell it to the military
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.68,0:14:24.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想象一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:24.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Imagine--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.75,0:14:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,火焰喷射器燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fuel for flamethrowers
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,杀手机器人润滑油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lubricant for killer robots
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.67,0:14:33.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发出薯条香气的炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:33.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bombs that smell like French fries
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.74,0:14:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就用这油来增进蟹堡王的生意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll use it to boost business at The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.30,0:14:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可口的全新三明治配料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a flavorful new sandwich topping
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:40.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1184,620)}美味
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃的全新奶昔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a savory new milkshake
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有厕所的全新芳香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and a lovely new scent for the restrooms
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能用我的油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.79,0:14:51.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not using my grease
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.74,0:14:54.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你家蟹堡王拉客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:54.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to drive customers to your restaurant
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.59,0:14:55.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:55.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.09,0:14:56.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:56.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I ought to
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, gosh, I don't see
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.18,0:15:03.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们为什么非得只找一种用途
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:03.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why you need to find just one use for this stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.44,0:15:06.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我所有用途全都要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:06.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I started using it for everything
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牙膏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toothpaste
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,沐浴露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bodywash
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除臭剂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,deodorant
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鞋油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,shoe polish
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能敷一整晚的面膜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all-night face mask
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1304,848)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗的早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary's breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.15,0:15:17.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己的早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:17.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my own breakfast
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:18.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1304,848)}我自己
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还治好了我滑囊炎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It even cured my bursitis
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.90,0:15:21.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:21.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I mean is
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.92,0:15:24.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你们所有用途全都要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:24.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you can use it for anything
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.12,0:15:26.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然就把它当万能神油卖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:26.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,why not sell it for everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:34.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,922)}蟹痞博士奇迹万能神油
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.08,0:15:35.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:35.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.30,0:15:38.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好引点客人来  尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:38.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we better get some customers here, Eugene
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.12,0:15:40.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我熬夜一整晚画了那个牌子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:40.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was up all night painting that sign
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点信心嘛  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have a little faith, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.87,0:15:46.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  午餐高峰期
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:46.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold, the lunch rush
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.07,0:16:04.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该来干活了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:04.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to get to work
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.35,0:16:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要买点蟹痞博士奇迹万能神油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but how about some
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dr. Krabton's Miracle Everything Juice
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你的小天使们静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:16.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to quiet the little angels?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.16,0:16:29.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹痞博士可以帮你把船修好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:29.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, Dr. Krabton can fix up your boat for you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.19,0:16:32.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:32.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.15,0:16:32.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完好如初
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:32.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good as new
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真的有用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, it really works
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.55,0:16:38.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为万能神油欢呼三声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:38.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three cheers for Everything Juice
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要买一份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll take one
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.45,0:16:53.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看咱赚了这么多钱  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:53.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all this cash, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们发财了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're rich
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.42,0:16:56.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不够发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:16:56.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not rich enough
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.22,0:16:58.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要开始巡回演出了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:58.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got to take our show on the road
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我这个真正的推销员给你好好示范
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let a real salesman show you how it's done
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.20,0:17:10.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可太惊喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:10.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天没约我出去吃午餐  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't have a lunch date today, do we?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是跟我约
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not with me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.82,0:17:17.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是要跟划算约
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:17.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your date today is with value
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.30,0:17:20.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假如我告诉你有一样产品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:20.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Suppose I told you there was one product
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以给你所有船都加上油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that could fuel all your boats
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方便重新粉刷旧灯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reinvigorate old lighthouse paint jobs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.08,0:17:34.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能覆盖住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:34.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And even cover up those
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,眼睛周围的皱纹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:38.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maturation lines around your eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.87,0:17:39.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我抹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:39.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plank
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么敢这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How dare you?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.70,0:17:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我来十瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me ten bottles
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你表现可太好了  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did pretty good back there, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.57,0:17:51.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过现在得瞧瞧大师的本领
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:51.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But now it's time to watch a master
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.64,0:17:53.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:53.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gladly
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等他来了再提醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me know when he gets here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.75,0:17:58.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.75,0:17:58.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Greetings, Sandra
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.40,0:18:03.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来这是要向你介绍我们最新发明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:03.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am here to tell you about our latest invention
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以帮你的草地施肥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll fertilize your lawn
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,擦亮你的树屋玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Polish your dome glass
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能让你最老的坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And give even your oldest nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.69,0:18:19.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,焕发出新鲜采摘的光泽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:19.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that fresh-picked shine
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.82,0:18:26.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是蟹痞博士奇迹万能神油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:26.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Dr. Krabton's Miracle Everything Juice
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不是土包子  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't some hayseed, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是科学家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:33.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a scientist
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.21,0:18:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不相信奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't believe in miracles
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.87,0:18:37.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它还能让制氧机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:37.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, but it can also keep oxygen machines
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.63,0:18:38.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工作在最佳状态
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:38.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,running in top shape
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.77,0:18:46.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒挺喜欢呼吸的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:46.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I do like breathin'
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我买一整箱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take a whole case
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.62,0:18:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上门推销耗的时间太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This door-to-door stuff's taking too long
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.62,0:18:53.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须玩得更大点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:53.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got to go big
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么个大法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How big?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盛大音乐剧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Musical big
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:04.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(814,140)}蟹痞博士奇迹万能神油
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.32,0:19:07.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好先生  想不想了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:07.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, there, mister, would you like to know
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一样特别神奇的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,About a very a special something
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.45,0:19:11.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你烦恼都消散
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:11.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That makes all your problems go away?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.72,0:19:12.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.42,0:19:13.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是万能神油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:13.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Everything Juice
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.58,0:19:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好大姐  我能不能帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, there, madam, can I help you out
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.60,0:19:18.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮你洗洗假牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:18.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With those false teeth of yours
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.07,0:19:20.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想必你一定难以欢呼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:20.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It must be very hard to shout hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.11,0:19:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,庆祝万能神油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For Everything Juice
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.62,0:19:26.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能让我声音听着更可怕点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:26.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can it make my voice sound much more creepy?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.59,0:19:27.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大概行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:27.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Probably
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.39,0:19:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能让我家琪琪不发臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will it fix the smell of my pet Kiki?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买一买瞧一瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Buy it and see
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.15,0:19:32.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:32.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,孩子们好  你们好像很需要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, there, son, looks like you might need
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到滑腻腻的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To find some slickening solution
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.85,0:19:40.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你们弹珠滚得飞快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:40.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So your marbles can get up to speed today
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,试试万能神油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try Everything Juice
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我发现你比较想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, but I see you chose
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,留着长长的鼻毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not to trim that rather lengthy hair
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.22,0:19:49.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长到探出鼻孔  但没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.22,0:19:49.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Protruding from your nose, but that's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有万能神油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With Everything Juice
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.82,0:19:52.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这要多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:52.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much does it cost?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.55,0:19:53.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:53.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quite a lot
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't care
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,存货全都卖给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me everything you've got
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的  我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, my friends
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.02,0:19:59.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西一级棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:19:59.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is the greatest stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是个天大的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a wonder, it's a miracle
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要多少都不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just can't have enough
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.52,0:20:04.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就快来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:04.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So we say hey
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上来买
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get some today
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不需要借口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no excuse
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.90,0:20:11.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都需要万能神油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:11.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone needs Everything Juice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:19.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(832,470)}蟹痞博士
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.12,0:20:16.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一百万零一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:16.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A million one
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一百万零二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a million two
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一百万零三
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a million three
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.25,0:20:24.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤金  这就是友情的感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:24.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eugene, is this what friendship feels like?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.08,0:20:26.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该就是了  谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:26.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it is, Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.92,0:20:28.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:28.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it is
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.05,0:20:30.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扔钱大战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:30.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money fight
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.49,0:20:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们来这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you all doing in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.81,0:20:43.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是不满意的顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:43.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are unsatisfied customers
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你家油对我空气干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at what your grease did to my air
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.91,0:20:53.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你家油害我眼睛都红肿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:53.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your grease gave me pink eye
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.98,0:20:55.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:55.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least your
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.84,0:20:58.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皱纹没了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:20:58.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maturation lines are gone
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要再买两瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:01.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take two more bottles
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.57,0:21:06.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个已经把全裤头村都毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:06.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two have ruined the whole town
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.91,0:21:09.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要退钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:09.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We want our money back
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会搞砸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew you would mess this up
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.07,0:21:19.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你老是把事情都搞砸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:19.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You always mess things up
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.32,0:21:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.12,0:21:23.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才没想出那首破歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:23.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not the one who came up with that lousy song
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.59,0:21:29.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定是油量不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:29.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must be running low on grease
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.75,0:21:32.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:32.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it wasn't me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.30,0:21:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把它当灭火器补充液卖的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who sold it as fire extinguisher recharging fluid
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.90,0:21:36.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:36.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.87,0:21:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可又不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm not the one
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.55,0:21:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把它卖给中学生治青春痘的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who sold it as acne treatment to high schoolers
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.92,0:21:46.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你确实把它当饮用维生素卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:46.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you did market it as drinkable vitamins
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.49,0:21:47.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:47.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.93,0:21:50.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这场友情结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:50.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This friendship is over
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.37,0:21:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又要来当死对头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are mortal enemies once more
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.92,0:21:54.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:54.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine by me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.36,0:21:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不想见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.36,0:21:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see you ever again, ever
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.30,0:22:08.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:08.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is all your fault
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.27,0:22:10.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害咱困在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.27,0:22:10.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You trapped us in here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.92,0:22:13.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望我从来没见过你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:13.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I'd never met you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.19,0:22:15.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我加倍希望没见过你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.19,0:22:15.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That goes double for me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.49,0:22:16.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:16.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.65,0:22:20.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三位好朋友一起被活埋一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:20.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The three best friends buried alive together forever
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.82,0:22:22.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都多亏了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:22.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it's all thanks to
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.87,0:22:25.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万能神油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.87,0:22:25.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything Juice
